[
    {
        "block": "About",
        "name": "Introduction",
        "chapters": [
            {
                "blockname": "Introduction",
                "name": "Introduction",
                "sections": [
                    {
                        "subtitle": "Welcome to this tutorial",
                        "space_after": false,
                        "components": [
                            {
                                "type": "text-paragraph",
                                "links": [
                                    {
                                        "portion": "Heroku",
                                        "href": "https://www.heroku.com/home"
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "portion": "GitHub",
                                        "href": "https://github.com/"
                                    }
                                ],
                                "text": "In this tutorial, you will learn how to deploy your own version of this website. This tutorial will teach you how to deploy using Heroku, which is a very straight-forward service, very easy to use and FREE! You will also use GitHub, to download the website to your account and to upload the website to Heroku."
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text-alert",
                                "text": "This tutorial will only talk about deploying with Heroku. If you want to deploy your website on a local server, check the Github description page for the website linked below."
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "link-website",
                                "links": [
                                    {
                                        "text": "Github page for this website",
                                        "link": "https://github.com/ovidium19/SupportForStudents"
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text-paragraph",
                                "links": [],
                                "text": "This tutorial will also teach you how to use the various tools available on the website to edit its content. You can use the admin features to create your own version of content, embed links, images, videos and all sorts of components with minimal effort."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "subtitle": "Learning Outcomes",
                        "space_after": false,
                        "components": [
                            {
                                "type": "list-text",
                                "list_elements": [
                                    {
                                        "links": [
                                            {
                                                "portion": "Heroku",
                                                "href": "https://www.heroku.com/home"
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "portion": "Github",
                                                "href": "https://github.com/"
                                            }
                                        ],
                                        "text": "In this chapter, we will simply create a Heroku and a Github account. These tools will be needed in order to download the website to your Github account and upload it to Heroku, which is a cloud server that will make your website available for other users to see for FREE!"
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "blockname": "Introduction",
                "name": "Prerequisites",
                "sections": [
                    {
                        "subtitle": "Github",
                        "space_after": false,
                        "components": [
                            {
                                "type": "text-paragraph",
                                "links": [
                                    {
                                        "portion": "Github",
                                        "href": "https://github.com/"
                                    }
                                ],
                                "text": "First, you will need a Github account. Go to their website(linked in the name) and create an account. This is a simple process resembling all other sign-up forms you have probably used before.",
                                "space_after": true
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text-paragraph",
                                "links": [],
                                "text": "Once you have created the account, you should login. Your landing page will look something like this."
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "image-single",
                                "src": "images/github_landing.jpg",
                                "space_after": true
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text-paragraph",
                                "links": [],
                                "text": "You can read the guide for a bit to understand what github does, but for the purpose of this tutorial, it is not necessary."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "subtitle": "Heroku",
                        "space_after": false,
                        "components": [
                            {
                                "type": "text-paragraph",
                                "links": [
                                    {
                                        "portion": "Heroku",
                                        "href": "https://id.heroku.com/login"
                                    }
                                ],
                                "text": "We will do the same with Heroku. Create an account and then log in.",
                                "space_after": true
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text-paragraph",
                                "links": [],
                                "text": "The landing page will look something like this."
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "image-single",
                                "src": "images/heroku_landing.jpg"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text-paragraph",
                                "links": [],
                                "text": "You can click the 'New' Button and then 'Create New App'. This will prompt you to the second screen which looks like this."
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "image-single",
                                "src": "images/heroku_create.jpg"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text-paragraph",
                                "links": [],
                                "text": "The name you choose will be the name of you website. For example, if you choose test-server-2018, then the name of your website will be https://test-server-2018.herokuapp.com"
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "blockname": "Introduction",
                "name": "Summary",
                "sections": [
                    {
                        "subtitle": "Before you go on...",
                        "space_after": false,
                        "components": [
                            {
                                "type": "text-paragraph",
                                "links": [],
                                "text": "Try to have your Github and Heroku accounts set up. In Heroku, you can also create your new app at this point and name it however you want.\nThese are necessities in order to continue to the next chapter."
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
